I got a family to feed.

52:25.446 --> 52:26.491
Okay, who is it?

52:28.580 --> 52:30.712
Babe, I'm not seein' anyone--

52:30.843 --> 52:32.584
Who is she? Don't touch me.

52:32.714 --> 52:33.846
Who is she?

52:33.976 --> 52:35.543
Are you gonna do this right now?

52:35.674 --> 52:37.980
