Can you go get me some water?

52:45.074 --> 52:47.381
Go get me water.

52:47.512 --> 52:48.774
You want cold or room temp?

52:51.124 --> 52:53.518
Come on, you can't stay mad
at me. I'll get you some water.

52:53.648 --> 52:54.823
