52:54.954 --> 52:57.391
[groans]
Stop.

52:59.654 --> 53:00.699
[sighs]

53:07.227 --> 53:08.489
Hey, how you doin'?

53:10.099 --> 53:11.797
Do I know you, man?

53:11.927 --> 53:14.582
Hey, man, how'd you like to earn
an easy 50,000?

53:15.975 --> 53:17.846
What are you talkin' about?

53:17.977 --> 53:19.718
I know who you work for.

53:19.848 --> 53:21.720
I just want one photo, man.

53:21.850 --> 53:24.244
