58:22.063 --> 58:25.327
- No. No, no, no!
- Just a little bit.

58:25.458 --> 58:28.461
- Paris, you got to eat.
- I don't want soup!

58:28.592 --> 58:31.246
- Then what do you want?
- I want to go home.

58:31.377 --> 58:33.205
