to take a bath and go to bed.

01:02:42.759 --> 01:02:44.978
- Bedtime. Bedtime.
- Good night.

01:02:45.109 --> 01:02:47.154
- Thank you. Good night.
- 'I don't wanna go to bed.'

01:02:47.285 --> 01:02:49.243
- How was your flight?
- No flight.

01:02:49.374 --> 01:02:52.507
